<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="536" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="0.[1237,2119,845,1470]" pageId="0" pageNumber="536">• Small to medium-sized rodents with mouse-shaped skulls; squirrel-shaped mandibles; and mostly long, naked tails equal to or longer than head-body lengths.</paragraph>
