<paragraph blockId="0.[1237,2119,845,1470]" box="[1233,1888,1316,1345]" pageId="0" pageNumber="536">• All terrestrial and some aquatic habitats.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1237,2119,845,1470]" box="[1237,2005,1355,1384]" pageId="0" pageNumber="536">• 155 genera, 816 species, at least 916 extant taxa.</paragraph>
